Message.SourceString: I generally discourage violence, but this time I think you need to gather as much of it as possible and serve up a dragon sized portion.
Message.LocalizedString: I generally discourage violence, but this time I think you need to gather as much of it as possible and serve up a dragon sized portion.

Message.SourceString: Build the horn. Summon Velgar. Avenge Cathan, save us all. Punch a dragon in the face!
Message.LocalizedString: Build the horn. Summon Velgar. Avenge Cathan, save us all. Punch a dragon in the face!

Message.SourceString: So, first off, death sucks. Let's just get that out of the way. I figured I might at least stand a chance against Velgar, I had all the plans, and I am sure I could have beaten him.
Message.LocalizedString: So, first off, death sucks. Let's just get that out of the way. I figured I might at least stand a chance against Velgar, I had all the plans, and I am sure I could have beaten him.

Message.SourceString: Cathan's dead? To shreds you say? Poor lad, not the end he deserved. But Velgar's made a mistake here, he's made this personal.
Message.LocalizedString: Cathan's dead? To shreds you say? Poor lad, not the end he deserved. But Velgar's made a mistake here, he's made this personal.

Message.SourceString: But then his garou minions mobbed me and dragged me here. They held me down as Velgar watched, laughing as they sacrificed me!
Message.LocalizedString: But then his garou minions mobbed me and dragged me here. They held me down as Velgar watched, laughing as they sacrificed me!

Message.SourceString: Here, let me teach you a recipe. It's a dragonkin horn that will force Velgar to battle. It's got to be used here, in an altar on the tower, but Velgar can't refuse it.
Message.LocalizedString: Here, let me teach you a recipe. It's a dragonkin horn that will force Velgar to battle. It's got to be used here, in an altar on the tower, but Velgar can't refuse it.

Message.SourceString: Make the horn, summon the dragon and then kick his ass for me. I'm counting on you, hero, we all are.
Message.LocalizedString: Make the horn, summon the dragon and then kick his ass for me. I'm counting on you, hero, we all are.

Message.SourceString: I need you to gear yourself up as best you can, then push into Ghornfel to look for young Cathan.
Message.LocalizedString: I need you to gear yourself up as best you can, then push into Ghornfel to look for young Cathan.

Message.SourceString: Make the horn, summon the dragon and then kick his ass for me. I'm counting on you, hero, we all are.
Message.LocalizedString: Make the horn, summon the dragon and then kick his ass for me. I'm counting on you, hero, we all are.

Message.SourceString: You did it! Velgar got what he deserved. Thank you, hero, now I can rest in peace.
Message.LocalizedString: You did it! Velgar got what he deserved. Thank you, hero, now I can rest in peace.

Message.SourceString: As death's go it could have been more heroic. Not exactly what I wanted on my epitaph. But, hey, silver cloud, you can avenge me now!
Message.LocalizedString: As death's go it could have been more heroic. Not exactly what I wanted on my epitaph. But, hey, silver cloud, you can avenge me now!

Message.SourceString: Ghornfell is a dangerous place, and home to the garou beastmen. Keep your wits about you.
Message.LocalizedString: Ghornfell is a dangerous place, and home to the garou beastmen. Keep your wits about you.

Message.SourceString: Make the horn, summon the dragon and then kick his ass for me. I'm counting on you, hero, we all are.
Message.LocalizedString: Make the horn, summon the dragon and then kick his ass for me. I'm counting on you, hero, we all are.

Message.SourceString: But if the entrance to Ghornfel is what you say, it sounds like Cathan has been captured...again... so I need you to go and rescue him.
Message.LocalizedString: But if the entrance to Ghornfel is what you say, it sounds like Cathan has been captured...again... so I need you to go and rescue him.

Message.SourceString: I imagine the garou will be taking him to Velgar. Make your way to the tower, and pray you're not too late.
Message.LocalizedString: I imagine the garou will be taking him to Velgar. Make your way to the tower, and pray you're not too late.

Message.SourceString: You've made it into Ghornfel, I'm impressed. No, honestly, I expected you to drown in the swamp or something.
Message.LocalizedString: You've made it into Ghornfel, I'm impressed. No, honestly, I expected you to drown in the swamp or something.

Properties.TextName: Look for evidence of Cathan at the tower
